  head Fail 3 attempts password log in
  title
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/main.css')
  script(src='/scripts/recovKey.js' nonce=nonce)
  body
  h1(data-name=usrInfo.name) Sorry! you have failed password logging in 3 attempts
  h2 You have two options, that are: 
  p 1. Use your recovery key to access all web credentials or 
  br
  label(for='recovKey') Please input your Recovery Key
  input#keyInput(type='text', name='recovKey', placeholder='RECOVERY KEY', size='50')
  br  
  button#recovKey Submit Key
  br
  br
  p 2. Reset and set new password, but will not be able to access your existing web credentials.
  div#pwReset
  form(action='/pwReset', method='post')
     input(type='radio', checked, name='resetPw', value='yes')
     | Reset password
     br
     br
     input(type='radio', name='resetPw', value='no')
     | No Reset (back to login page)
     br
     br
     button(type='submit') Submit
     input#mail(type = 'hidden', name = 'email', value=`${usrEmPh.email}`)
     input#phone(type = 'hidden', name = 'phone', value = `${usrEmPh.phone}`)
     input#maskM(type = 'hidden', name = 'maskEmail', value=`${maskUsrEmPh.email}`)
     input#maskM(type = 'hidden', name = 'maskPhone', value=`${maskUsrEmPh.phone}`)
     input#usrId(type = 'hidden', name = 'id', value =`${usrInfo.id}`)
     input#name(type = 'hidden', name = 'name', value =`${usrInfo.name}`)
     input#authTok(type = 'hidden', name = 'auTok', value = `${authTok}`)
  br
  br
  footer
      p The entirety of this site is protected by copyright @2024 1FirstPass company limited
      address 84/23 Ratchapruek28 Road, Talingchan, Bangkok 10170, Thailand
      p
      colspan 
          a(href='/tnc') Terms&Conditions  
      colspan 
          a(href='/privPo') Privacy Policy